Subject: Performance: Derwood Bowen + 2d6
Description:
An up-and-comer from Westerville, OH, Derwood Bowen has been recording comedy songs, including parody songs, for 10 years, and has been a frequent contributor to the Sideshow at thefump.com. 2d6's rhymes are about the geekiest of geek topics: anime conventions, Boba Fett, Amedeo Avogadro, daikaiju, geek girls, and the like.
